    12| * mounted rAF loop), so they are NOT stored here.
    13| *
    14| * Emit is deferred to a microtask — render-warning interception runs while React
    15| * is rendering, so calling subscriber setState synchronously would reproduce the
    16| * exact "Cannot update a component while rendering a different component" warning
    17| * this screen exists to catch. Deferring moves every subscriber update out of the
    18| * render phase (same pattern as ivxAIWatchdog).
